# This is a comment
:put "hello" # inline comment
	# indented comment

----------------------------------------------------

[
	["comment", "# This is a comment"],

	["prefix", ":"],
	["command", "put"],
	["string", ["\"hello\""]],
	["comment", "# inline comment"],

	["comment", "# indented comment"]
]

----------------------------------------------------

Tests the `comment` token: standalone line comments, inline comments after code,
and indented comments.
